OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,6,Fsome showery, perhaps thundery, rain
OL,7,Faround. Becoming brighter from the
OL,8,Fsouth through the afternoon but still
OL,9,Fsome showers around. Warm and humid.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAny showers dying out and
OL,12,Fsome evening sunshine expected,
OL,13,Ffreshening southwesterly winds.
OL,14,FClouding over with the risk of some
OL,15,Fshowers later in the night. Feeling
OL,16,Fquite muggy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
