OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA cloudy start to the
OL,6,Fweekend with some showers and fresh
OL,7,Fwinds, showers may turn heavy with
OL,8,Fsome thunder in the afternoon and
OL,9,Fevening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,12,FRemaining warm on Sunday and Monday
OL,13,Fbut with a freshening breeze, plenty
OL,14,Fof bright weather but scattered
OL,15,Fshowers. Dry and bright with lighter
OL,16,Fwinds on Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
